      <title>麦克莱姆认为移民改革对通胀影响不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/macklem-sees-little-inflation-impact-from-immigration-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂芙·麦克勒姆表示，联邦政府削减移民目标的决定虽然对经济增长产生温和影响，但对通胀的影响可能有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/macklem-sees-little-inflation-impact-from-immigration-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 18:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
