      <title>Nexus 获得 7.65 亿美元融资用于收购 Big Lots</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/nexus-gets-765-million-financing-for-big-lots-acquisition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私募股权公司 Nexus Capital Management 获得 7.65 亿美元承诺融资以支持其对破产折扣零售商 Big Lots Inc. 的收购计划，随后一名联邦法官批准其作为收购该零售商的主要竞标者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/nexus-gets-765-million-financing-for-big-lots-acquisition</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 18:16:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因争议，马里威胁让巴里克采矿许可证失效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/mali-threatens-to-let-barrick-mine-permit-lapse-over-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有关如何分配马里金矿经济利益的争议不断升级之际，马里军政府威胁要在 2026 年现有许可证到期时收回巴里克黄金公司 (Barrick Gold Corp.) 的 Loulo 矿特许权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/mali-threatens-to-let-barrick-mine-permit-lapse-over-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 18:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
